                            <div class="col-lg-4 carousel slide" id="bannerCarouselBlock132349" data-ride="carousel">
                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                                                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                                                                    <h2>A GlobalSign Podcast : TrustID Talk</h2>
                                                                                                    <p>Michelle Davidson is joined by Jane Frankland, CEO of KnewStart, and Lila Kee, Chief Product Officer at GlobalSign. Together, they discuss the evolving role of women in cybersecurity</p>
                                                                                                    <a href="https://www.globalsign.com/en/podcast"> Listen to the podcast </a>
                                                            </div>
                                                    <div class="carousel-item ">
                                                                    <h2>The Best Identity Integrations for Added Flexibility</h2>
                                                                                                    <p>A comprehensive network of trusted technology solutions</p>
                                                                                                    <a href="https://www.globalsign.com/en/partner/service-providers"> Explore our network </a>
                                                            </div>
                                                    <div class="carousel-item ">
